snippet.title: Space Commanders 2 gameplay (PC Game, 1985)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Space Commanders 2, Dos PC game produced by Columbia Data Products in 1985 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/space-commanders-2/679/
Your mission in the game is to shoot as many enemies as possible before they reach you. Control your spaceship and shoot at alien creatures as well as their ships at the highest screen levels.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
